text-foreground/60 font-inter max-w-2xl mx-auto\">While traditional agencies charge $50k+ upfront, our SaaS model guarantees premium infrastructure for a fraction of the cost.</p></div></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start\"><div class=\"relative rounded-[3rem] p-10 flex flex-col h-full border bg-secondary/30 border-border text-foreground\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-black tracking-tight mb-2\">Launchpad</h3><p class=\"font-inter text-foreground/60\">For startups &amp; MVPs</p></div><div class=\"mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-end gap-2 mb-2\"><span class=\"text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter\">$2,500</span></div><p class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground/40\">one-time setup</p><div class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-current/10\"><p class=\"font-bold text-xl\">$499/mo</p><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground/40\">Hosting &amp; Maintenance</p></div></div><ul class=\"space-y-4 mb-12 flex-grow\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 shrink-0 text-foreground/40\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-inter font-medium text-sm\">Next.js Architecture Setup</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 shrink-0 text-foreground/40\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4